      "B": "$-12x+6$",
      "C": "$x^2-2x+1$",
      "D": "$x^2+x+6$",
      "E": "$-x^2-x+6$"
    },
    "answer": "A",
    "solution": "Remainder $ax^2+bx+c$; $P(-1)=6\\Rightarrow a-b+c=6$; $b+a=-2$, $c-a=1\\Rightarrow a=1,b=-3,c=2$"
